message: My cat is stuck on a tree - please save her!
Got it. Where are you located?
Near the park on Herzl street.
Is the cat injured or just scared?
Not injured. She is scared and meowing.
How high is the tree? Approx meters?
About 4 meters. I can't reach her.
Stay calm. Keep people away and do not climb if unsafe.
Yes. Help is on the way. Keep an eye on her.
You're welcome. Update me if anything changes.
